	<div class="image">
				
							
									
					<img src="/var/knowledge/storage/images/media/images/jimma-university-college-of-agriculture-and-veterinary-medicine-jucavm/482752-1-eng-GB/Jimma-University-College-of-Agriculture-and-Veterinary-Medicine-JUCAVM_dossierfront.jpg" />
